pulseaudio_interface
====================

Small, bash based script which allows controlling pulseaudio and displaying a osd via dzen2 or notify-osd

Usage: pulseaudio_interface.sh [-hgsmkidtnz]
-h			display this message
-g			get current volume
-s <value>	set volume to value
-m <yes|no>	set mute to value
-t			toggle mute
-k <sink>		select this sink
-i <value>	increase volume by value
-d <value>	decrease volume by value
-n			display volume using notify-osd
-z 			display volume using dzen2

